ortation to stanford area car rental shuttles to and from the airport supershuttle is a van service at san francisco airport that collects people along the upper departure level of any terminal on the center island outside of the airline ticket counters the one way charge is about $25 call 415 558 8500 south and east bay shuttle is a van service for san francisco or san jose airports call 800 548 4664 or 408 225 4444 caltrain from san francisco airport take the sfo bart extension to the millbrae intermodal station then caltrain to menlo park or palo alto call 800 660 4287 for schedules taxi services samtrans from san francisco airport take bus kx south it leaves every 30 minutes and takes about 55 minutes call 800 660 4287 for schedules marguerite shuttle the free marguerite shuttle has a line that runs to slac you can pick up a line a shuttle in palo alto and take it to the hoover tower stop where you transfer to the slac shuttle the slac shuttle runs every 20 minutes call 650 723 9362 for schedules the kavli foundation slac national accelerator laboratory stanford university privacy statement
